    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Yes its now documented, see: https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/documentation/#hits\n\nAlso see our example:\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/498577e4c3785c373c273913833ead5a90c7fbf7/dev/app.js#L53\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/498577e4c3785c373c273913833ead5a90c7fbf7/dev/index.html#L70\n- https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch.js/blob/498577e4c3785c373c273913833ead5a90c7fbf7/dev/templates/all-items.html\n\nAs you can see, you must create the table inside the template, it can't be the main container.\n",
